data.description: LEGAL 2 FAMILY - DELIVERED VACANT! Centrally located and close to all. Come take a tour of 141-08 123rd Ave. in Jamaica, Queens. This property has a building size of 20' x 50' and boasts 3 bedrooms, over 3 bedrooms, and a full walk-out, apartment sized basement. Wow! This semi-detached home is in move-in condition and offers 3 separate floors, each with plenty of space. The 1st floor is a full apartment with 3 bedrooms, and the 2nd floor is also a full apartment with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The basement includes 1 family room and 2 additional rooms. This home has Solar Panels with a current Lease, which the new owner would have to assume. However, the current owner is able to get a $1600 Property Tax Reduction with Solar! Don't Wait - This property has a lot of space for your family and to generate $$$ Rental Income!
